  "title": "Flaming Swords",
  "description": "Makes the Fire Aspect Enchantment show flames",
  "body": "<center>\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/EcjQY7O3/images/bec8993225998c596614286151f92c57ecc3435c.png\" width=\"700\" alt=\"Flaming Swords Logo\"><br>\n\n## Makes the Fire Aspect Enchantment show flames\n<br>\n\n[![View the pack on my website!](https://img.shields.io/badge/View%20the%20pack%20on%20my%20website!-black?style=for-the-badge)](https://mr-expence.github.io/projects/flaming-swords)\n<br><br>\n\nThis Resource pack changes the texture for swords when you enchant it with Fire Aspect.\n\nIt needs a cit mod for 1.21.4 or below as 1.21.5 adds custom item textures.\n\nThere are diffrent colours for the Copper and Netherite swords\n\n3D Mace and Bow from tixul's Enchantment Outlines\n\nFlaming Swords now has support for tixul's [Enchantment Outlines](https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/glowing-glints)\n\nYou can toggle the glowing using [ResPackOpts](https://modrinth.com/mod/respackopts)\n\nIf there is no animations try turning off `Animate Only Visible Textures` in the Video Settings\n<br><br><br>\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/EcjQY7O3/images/70dcc47e7860c1707760ca2fcf62bc2d765519c7.png\" width=\"600\" alt=\"Flame Bow\"><br><br>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/EcjQY7O3/images/3737ca4784006ee1c70831472aa744299bbb3755.png\" width=\"600\" alt=\"Flame Bow Pulling\"><br><br>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/EcjQY7O3/images/45f656c2abc79665026a7b4c58e6802cbbfcc14e.png\" width=\"600\" alt=\"Bow Pulling\"><br><br>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/EcjQY7O3/images/c082ffe7a9a9fd885ad645c77332c7b2cdacc34b.png\" width=\"600\" alt=\"Copper Sword\"><br><br>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/EcjQY7O3/images/d1ed04f5bb75de65a8cd7ec4dae08e1779ca0151.png\" width=\"600\" alt=\"Diamond Sword\"><br><br>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/EcjQY7O3/images/6751d00de6e17d2d8d76945e3c2ad29a824b75d6.png\" width=\"600\" alt=\"Golden Sword\"><br><br>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/EcjQY7O3/images/7197d9cf6dd9169672cb74531dfa038e19deb243.png\" width=\"600\" alt=\"Iron Sword\"><br><br>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/EcjQY7O3/images/3af7d717b77baf619c9109336a7dd1abc59d4af9.png\" width=\"600\" alt=\"Fire Aspect Mace\"><br><br>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/EcjQY7O3/images/b7a59aa7907056baa50b29f9675de16be4ec1b9e.png\" width=\"600\" alt=\"Flat Fire Aspect Mace\"><br><br>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/EcjQY7O3/images/108d9d64c0d460eafbc674b372a3ddc91df7c75e.png\" width=\"600\" alt=\"3D Mace\"><br><br>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/EcjQY7O3/images/c6c55f008fb144232ead513181cc89047596058b.png\" width=\"600\" alt=\"Netherite Sword\"><br><br>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/EcjQY7O3/images/d49157423abd5c0ea4bc3ff05a7a7300407fdd52.png\" width=\"600\" alt=\"Stone Sword\"><br><br>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/EcjQY7O3/images/b153adfb7322d685f70310d5a863d31033468512.png\" width=\"600\" alt=\"Wooden Sword\"><br><br>\n<br><br>\nAll my projects that have been uploaded on Modrinth, Curseforge, and PlanetMinecraft have All Rights Reserved.\r\n\r\nCopyright © 2025-present Mr_Expence\n</center>",
